  "text": "Linkage analysis was performed using MapMaker version 3.0b [CITATION_1] . Map distances were computed with the Kosambi mapping function. The map was initially constructed at a LOD of 3.0. Additional markers were added using the TRY command and their order was re ned using the RIPPLE command.",
